speaking_flexible.analysis_prompt_template:
Review learner answer in {language} for communicative adequacy. Question: {question}
Expected answer: {expected_answer}
Accepted answers: {accepted_answers}
Student answer: {user_answer}
Return exactly one JSON object with keys score, tips, sample_answers, question_variants. No markdown, no code fences, no extra text. sample_answers and question_variants must be arrays of plain strings, never objects. Generate 2-3 sample_answers and 2-3 question_variants. Build from learner answer toward a higher-scoring full answer. Do not repeat learner answer unchanged. Allow alternative valid responses when meaning is correct.

